  "instructions": [
    "Toast the slices of gluten-free bread and let them cool.",
    "In a small bowl, mix tahini paste, garlic, scallions, red pepper flakes, water, and vegetable oil until smooth.",
    "Warm a pan over medium heat and add the mixture from step 2 to it.",
    "Add cooled toast slices on top of the sauce. Cook for about 3 minutes or until golden brown on both sides.",
    "Serve hot with additional tahini sauce if desired."
